title: Лена Кука
overview: Lena Kuka - a sketch show from the eponymous team of Rustam Reptiloid and tambi Masayev, participants of KVN and winners of the show "Comedy battle". Together with them, absurd and at the same time very funny sketches are created by Mir Kashkov, Ilya Makarov, Alexey Shcherbakov and invited guests, including Nurlan Saburov.
